        <num>CCP 4849</num>
        <heading>4849.  Jurisdiction over the person</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 4849.  Jurisdiction over the person
A parish court or a city court may exercise jurisdiction over the person to the same extent, and in the same manner, as a district court.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
